These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: begonia, azalea
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, social-worker
2 different pets are kept: hamster, rat
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: animation, satire
1. the person who growsbegonia is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
3. the designer is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Flower       | azalea       | begonia |
| Job         | social-worker | designer  |
| Pet       | rat    | hamster    |
| Movie-Genre   | satire       | animation      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
There 2 different types of food: zucchini, cauliflower
There are 2 different nationalities: australian, brazilian
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: january, november
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: snowboarding, surfing
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the australian is on the far left##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Food      | cauliflower     | zucchini |
| Nationality           | australian | brazilian      |
| Birthday   | november  | january      |
| Sport         | snowboarding | surfing     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, soy-milk
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: september, june
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, blend
2 different pets are kept: goat, fish
1. the blend-smoker is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is the owner of the fish##1
3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | soy-milk  |
| Birthday          | september    | june   |
| Cigar   | blend  | tiparillo   |
| Pet     | fish     | goat |

