.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, soy-milk
There are 2 different favourite colors: mauve, coral
The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, bus
House: victorian, townhouse
1. the victorian house is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is the person who likes mauve##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea       | soy-milk |
| Color          | coral         | mauve    |
| Transport           | bus | ship    |
| House   | victorian           | townhouse   |

